# ============================================================================
# 01J: STEALER EVASION & ANTI-ANALYSIS NETWORK INDICATORS
# ============================================================================
# Network indicators of stealer sandbox/VM detection and evasion mechanisms
# ============================================================================

# --- system_profiler Network Callback ---
# AMOS runs system_profiler for sandbox/VM detection
# If VM detected, network activity stops — this rule catches
# ongoing exfiltration after VM check (VM check failed = real victim)
alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"CGTI-OC AMOS - System Profiler Data in Exfiltration"; flow:established,to_server; http.method; content:"POST"; http.request_body; content:"SPHardwareDataType"; content:"serial_number"; distance:0; within:300; classtype:trojan-activity; priority:1; metadata:malware_family AMOS, mitre_attack T1082, signature_severity Critical, false_positive Very_Low, deployment_note macOS system profiler data in POST body is highly suspicious; sid:9200110; rev:1;)


